  "title": "Operations Manager",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a responsible and dedicated Operations Executive to manage our fleet of vehicles. Job scope as follows:</p><ul><li>Compile all bookings and place on the booking system</li><li>Schedule assignements for driver</li><li>Follow up with drivers on all assignments and ensure all are punctual services are delivered</li><li>Plan and maintain all vehicle inspection, road tax/Insurance renewal</li><li>Conduct check on vehicles for safety and ensure vehicle are up to standards. Report to office on defects</li><li>Ensure daily movements are updated and send to accounts deparment</li></ul><p>Candidate must have decent knowledge of Windows and Excel. Good in English.</p><p>Company will provide mobile and computer. Incentives,Medical,Bonuses and annual leave will be given.</p><ul><li>Intrested candidates, kindly Whatsapp: 90053861 or 94558268</li></ul>",
